      <scopecontent id="aspace_03c7f453ce46b261608bf7c089cd0195">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, subject files, news clippings, photographs and sound recordings documenting the Yale Sheffield Scientific School Class of 1929 and its reunions.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
